      <title>铁路公司敦促边境官员重新开放美墨过境点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/railroads-urge-border-officials-to-reopen-us-mexico-crossings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铁路部门呼吁美国海关和边境保护局重新开放德克萨斯州埃尔帕索和伊格尔帕斯的美墨铁路过境点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/railroads-urge-border-officials-to-reopen-us-mexico-crossings</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 18:54:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管流动性紧缩，厄瓜多尔仍承诺偿还债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/ecuador-pledges-to-repay-its-debts-even-amid-liquidity-crunch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔财政部长胡安·卡洛斯·维加周一表示，尽管年底收支紧缩，但厄瓜多尔新政府仍致力于偿还国内外债务，并试图利用他首次公开露面的机会安抚对该国财政状况感到焦虑的投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/ecuador-pledges-to-repay-its-debts-even-amid-liquidity-crunch</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 18:42:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>胡塞武装袭击开始导致红海商船关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/houthi-attacks-start-shutting-down-red-sea-merchant-shipping</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于与以色列-哈马斯战争有关的暴力可能破坏全球经济，红海航运陷入停滞，油轮闲置，集装箱在非洲周围改道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/houthi-attacks-start-shutting-down-red-sea-merchant-shipping</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 18:11:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登对非法合并的打击与新政规则相结合</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/us-antitrust-agencies-cement-merger-crackdown-with-new-deal-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府的反垄断机构完成了对政府用来确定交易是否违反竞争法的规则的全面改革，以扩大对非法并购的打击力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/us-antitrust-agencies-cement-merger-crackdown-with-new-deal-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 17:44:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲观察家称塞尔维亚选举有利于执政党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/serbia-s-election-favored-ruling-party-european-observers-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲观察家称，塞尔维亚周日提前举行的选举因违规行为、媒体偏见和滥用国家资源而受到损害，这些因素导致选举偏向总统亚历山大·武契奇(Aleksandar Vucic)领导的执政党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/serbia-s-election-favored-ruling-party-european-observers-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 17:30:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为英语委员会提供资金增加未能缓解破产恐惧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/funding-boost-for-english-councils-fails-to-ease-bankruptcy-fear</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相苏纳克政府表示，英国议会明年将获得 6.5% 的资金支持，以帮助他们应对不断飙升的成本，但此举未能平息人们对即将到来的破产浪潮日益增长的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/funding-boost-for-english-councils-fails-to-ease-bankruptcy-fear</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 17:29:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰陆军参谋长敦促加快征召新兵以击退俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/ukraine-army-chief-urges-faster-conscription-to-repel-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总司令批评，面对西方援助的不确定性和俄罗斯扩大本国军队规模的举措，目前征召新兵的步伐太慢。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/ukraine-army-chief-urges-faster-conscription-to-repel-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 16:27:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国计划举行高层会谈应对胡塞武装红海威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/us-announces-plan-for-ministerial-meeting-to-meet-houthi-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀周二宣布计划召集部长级会议，讨论胡塞叛乱分子对红海商船的袭击事件数量不断增加的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/us-announces-plan-for-ministerial-meeting-to-meet-houthi-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 16:26:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼警告乌克兰军事援助基金将于 12 月 30 日耗尽</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/pentagon-warns-ukraine-military-aid-funds-will-run-out-dec-30</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼表示，除非国会批准新的资金，否则到 12 月 30 日将耗尽用于更换运往乌克兰的武器的资金，这也是五角大楼首次给出了现金耗尽的准确日期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/pentagon-warns-ukraine-military-aid-funds-will-run-out-dec-30</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 15:44:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布基纳法索因黄金产量下降而更换矿业部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/burkina-faso-names-new-mining-minister-in-government-reshuffle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布基纳法索的军事领导人易卜拉欣·特拉奥雷（Ibrahim Traore）任命了一位新的矿业和能源部长，此前该西非国家的安全担忧抑制了黄金生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/burkina-faso-names-new-mining-minister-in-government-reshuffle</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 21:35:22 GMT</pubDate>
